This section defines the features and functionalities that are included in the Predictive Stock Management System. These features are essential to achieve the project objectives and meet stakeholder needs.

In-Scope Features

User authentication and secure login

Role-based access for admin and users

Stock-in and stock-out management

Real-time inventory tracking

Historical data storage

Demand prediction based on past data

Identification of fast-moving and slow-moving items

Low-stock alerts and notifications

Dashboard for stock insights and trends

Basic reporting and data visualization

These features focus on improving inventory planning and reducing manual effort. The system aims to support proactive decision-making rather than just record keeping.
